Paula Wilcox https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paula_Wilcox 0 Paula Wilcox (born 13 December 1949) is an English actress. She is best known for roles in TV shows such as Girlfriends, Upstart Crow, Mount Pleasant, Boomers, Emmerdale, The Smoking Room, The Queen’s Nose and Man About The House.
